-- Turkey's Alternatifbank mandates banks for $350 mln bond issue
-- By Ece Toksabay
-- Fri Jul 11, 2014 05:44AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, July 11 (Reuters) - Turkish lender Alternatifbank <ALNTF.IS> said on Friday it had mandated BOFA Merrill Lynch and Commerzbank for a dollar-denominated bond issue worth up to $350 million.

The bank made the announcement in a statement to the Istanbul stock exchange.